text:
A unique Street that is closed to traffic, housed with stalls that sells souvenirs
Lunar Chinese New Year Decorations,
Sweets, Ice-creams  etc.
Many authentic chinese food restaurants, souvenir stores, hindu temple, buddha temple, just close to chinatown mrt station

If you are in Singapore, do come by here. Nearest MRT - ChinaTown MRT , Exit (Pagoda Street). There are various shops, and many temporary make shift stalls being put up to see the Chinese New Year goodies, cookies, candies, decorations , fruits and others. Come and immerse in the festive mood. There is no better time to be here , to witness the locals trying to sell the goods, and other local buyers doing their new year shopping. Do buy the BBQ pork to try, and good to bring home as gift for your relatives and friends.
clean and lots of stuffs to see
